OL,3,CWarning to be 'extremely cautious'
OL,4,Cover roof scam costing thousands
OL,6,FRogue traders in Cornwall have been
OL,7,Ftricking vulnerable and elderly people
OL,8,Finto paying thousands of pounds for
OL,9,Fjobs that should only cost a fraction
OL,10,Fof that.
OL,12,FAccording to Trading Standards
OL,13,Fofficers, traders have been going door
OL,14,Fto door offering to clean roofs and
OL,15,Fdriveways with a jet wash.
OL,17,FThey have been offering a sample area,
OL,18,Fwhich then leaves residents feeling
OL,19,Fthey have to have the job completed
OL,20,Frather than leave it looking
OL,21,Funfinished.
