OL,3,CWarning to be 'extremely cautious'
OL,4,Cover roof scam costing thousands
OL,6,FThe victims are then asked to pay
OL,7,F#2,000 for something which should only
OL,8,Fcost a few hundred pounds. The traders
OL,9,Fhave been particularly targeting
OL,10,Felderly and vulnerable people.
OL,12,FGary Webster, group leader of Cornwall
OL,13,FCouncil's Trading Standards team,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The law requires that traders
OL,15,Fwho agree services at your home, must
OL,16,Fprovide written information about the
OL,17,Fcontract and services they are
OL,18,Foffering.
