OL,3,CWarning to be 'extremely cautious'
OL,4,Cover roof scam costing thousands
OL,6,F"This must include a 14-day cooling-
OL,7,Foff period in which you can change
OL,8,Fyour mind. They should not be
OL,9,Fpressuring residents to agree to start
OL,10,Fwork immediately."
OL,12,FCouncillor Martyn Alvey, cabinet
OL,13,Fmember with responsibility for Public
OL,14,FProtection at Cornwall Council, said:
OL,15,F"We urge residents to be extremely
OL,16,Fcautious of agreeing to work following
OL,17,Fa cold-call at the door.
